race.comment: The feature of the day now and TALKANCO (1) gets a more favourable set up today after a big effort in the Belgravia. The inside draw is a big tick today as she'll sit much closer than she did last time out. Won well fresh and she can bounce back to winning form. PLAYIN'IT SWEET (2) comes through a different formline where she took on the older horses in a 72+ and she held her own. Back to her won age and sex today looks ideal and she continues to raise the bar. Can bounce back to winning ways. ZOURUN RUN (6) was good first-up in the Belgravia and is expected to have come on from that performance. She looks well placed on the back of that effort and she remains down in the weights. Can make her presence felt again. OURGIRLCANRUN (9) bolted in last start and turned in a strong figure in the process. Tougher now but she looks up to the task. RIVA AQUARAMA (7) was strong from the back and ticks a few boxes out in trip now.
